        <num>CCP 1066</num>
        <heading>1066.  Action matured or acquired after pleading</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1066.  Action matured or acquired after pleading
An action which either matured or was acquired by the defendant in the principal action after answer may be presented, with the permission of the court, as a reconventional demand by supplemental pleading.</p>
        </content>
